lding the sum of top and back: flipping another one and comparing both sums player may proceed  if second sum is higher; lower?: don't take it, flip it back and take all others you flipped during your turn. If you flip a '10' turn ends immidiately not being allowed to take any cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
